{
  "texts": [
    "It demonstrates the potential to generate concise and coherent summaries from large amounts of textual data.",
    "Spell/grammar checkThe spell/grammar check feature in the project leverages the power of the T5 model for accurate and efficient error detection and correction.",
    "The aim of this feature is to assist users in improving the grammatical accuracy and fluency of their written text.",
    "To evaluate the performance of the Spell/Grammar check feature, a comprehensive set of experiments was conducted.",
    "A diverse range of texts with varying degrees of grammatical errors were used as input to the T5 model."
